    %% RHODS Operator deploys all components
    RHODS ==>|deploys & manages| Dashboard
    RHODS ==>|deploys & manages| NotebookCtrl
    RHODS ==>|deploys & manages| KServe
    RHODS ==>|deploys & manages| ModelMesh
    RHODS ==>|deploys & manages| ODHModelCtrl
    RHODS ==>|deploys & manages| DSP
    RHODS ==>|deploys & manages| TrainingOp
    RHODS ==>|deploys & manages| CodeFlare
    RHODS ==>|deploys & manages| KubeRay
    RHODS ==>|deploys & manages| Kueue
    RHODS ==>|deploys & manages| TrustyAI

    %% Kubernetes API dependencies (all operators)
    RHODS -->|reconciles CRs| K8sAPI
    Dashboard -->|creates CRs| K8sAPI
    NotebookCtrl -->|watches CRs| K8sAPI
    KServe -->|watches CRs| K8sAPI
    ModelMesh -->|watches CRs| K8sAPI
    ODHModelCtrl -->|watches CRs| K8sAPI
    DSP -->|watches CRs| K8sAPI
    TrainingOp -->|watches CRs| K8sAPI
    CodeFlare -->|watches CRs| K8sAPI
    KubeRay -->|watches CRs| K8sAPI
    Kueue -->|watches CRs| K8sAPI
    TrustyAI -->|watches CRs| K8sAPI

    %% User interface dependencies
    Dashboard -->|authenticates users| OpenShiftOAuth
    Dashboard -->|creates Notebooks| NotebookCtrl
    Dashboard -->|creates InferenceServices| KServe
    Dashboard -->|creates Pipelines| DSP

    %% Notebook workflow dependencies
    NotebookCtrl -->|uses| Workbenches
    NotebookCtrl -->|creates Routes| OpenShiftRouter
    NotebookCtrl -.->|optional Istio integration| Istio
    Workbenches -->|accesses datasets/models| S3
    Workbenches -->|clones repos| GitRepos
    Workbenches -->|installs packages| PackageRepos
    Workbenches -->|pulls images| ContainerRegistry

    %% Model serving dependencies
    KServe -->|serverless autoscaling| Knative
    KServe -->|traffic management| Istio
    KServe -->|model metadata| ModelRegistry
    KServe -->|model artifacts| S3
    ODHModelCtrl -->|watches| KServe
    ODHModelCtrl -->|creates Routes| OpenShiftRouter
    ODHModelCtrl -->|creates VirtualServices| Istio
    ODHModelCtrl -->|creates ServiceMonitors| Prometheus
    ModelMesh -->|model artifacts| S3
    ModelMesh -->|metrics| Prometheus

    %% Pipeline dependencies
    DSP -->|artifact storage| S3
    DSP -->|deploys models| KServe
    DSP -->|metadata storage| MariaDB[(MariaDB)]
    DSP -.->|optional workflow engine| ArgoWorkflows[Argo Workflows]
    DSP -.->|optional workflow engine| Tekton[Tekton Pipelines]

    %% Training dependencies
    TrainingOp -->|job queueing| Kueue
    TrainingOp -.->|gang scheduling| Volcano
    TrainingOp -->|saves models| S3
    TrainingOp -->|metrics| Prometheus

    %% Distributed computing dependencies
    CodeFlare -->|watches RayClusters| KubeRay
    CodeFlare -->|queues AppWrappers| Kueue
    CodeFlare -->|injects OAuth proxy| OpenShiftOAuth
    CodeFlare -.->|optional mTLS| Istio
    KubeRay -->|creates Ray pods| K8sAPI
    KubeRay -->|creates Routes| OpenShiftRouter
    KubeRay -->|data access| S3
    Kueue -->|queues training jobs| TrainingOp
    Kueue -->|queues Ray clusters| CodeFlare
    Kueue -.->|cluster autoscaling| ClusterAutoscaler[Cluster Autoscaler]

    %% Model monitoring dependencies
    TrustyAI -->|patches deployments| KServe
    TrustyAI -->|monitors| ModelMesh
    TrustyAI -->|fairness metrics| Prometheus

    %% Monitoring dependencies
    Prometheus -->|visualizes| Grafana
    Prometheus -->|alerts| Alertmanager
    Dashboard -->|metrics| Prometheus
    NotebookCtrl -->|metrics| Prometheus

    %% Certificate management
    CertManager -->|issues certs| Dashboard
    CertManager -->|issues certs| KServe
    CertManager -->|issues certs| ModelMesh
    Istio -->|auto-issues mTLS certs| KServe

